def_cn: 未受影响的；未被改变的
def_en: If someone or something is unaffected by an event or occurrence, they are not changed by it in any way.

def_cn: 不矫揉造作的；自然的；率真的
def_en: If you describe someone as unaffected, you mean that they are natural and genuine in their behaviour, and do not act as though they are more important than other people.
